<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: auto;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .subject-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .subject-table th, .subject-table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 8px;
    }
    .subject-table th {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Attendance Shortage Notification</h2>
    <p>Dear {{name}} (Reg No: {{regNo}}),</p>

    <p>This is to inform you that your attendance in the following subjects is below the required threshold.</p>

    <table class="subject-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Subject</th>
          <th>Attendance (%)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{{subjectDetails}}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>Your overall attendance is: <strong>{{overallAttendance}}%</strong></p>

    <p>Please make necessary efforts to improve your attendance to avoid academic issues.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      Regards,<br />
      Academic Affairs Cell<br />
      {{institutionName}}
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
